  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This evaluation has two connected aims. The first is to assess the performance of NDF in accordance with its mandate. The second is to assess NDF&apos;s potential future role as a joint Nordic financing instrument for development. 
The evaluation shall concern the mandate from 2009 and consider the financial base of the institution, the priorities of the Nordic countries, and recent international agreements (the 2030 Agenda, the SDGs and the Paris Agreement) in assessing the NDF&apos;s present role as a joint Nordic instrument in the international climate architecture as well as its potential future role, within climate change or other areas.</narrative>
  </description>
